Subject: [RFC][PATCH v3 07/55] atomic_open(): saner calling conventions (return dentry on success)
Date:   Sun,  1 Mar 2020 21:51:52 +0000
Message-Id: <20200301215240.873899-7-viro@ZenIV.linux.org.uk>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.24.1
